ENGLISH TRANSLATION This simple game is based on a TV-game that in Italy is
called 'La ruota della Fortuna', but I do not know the name of his American
version.  
The program has a little help, and I think that it is enough to play with
it.  
You must simply choose 1 up to 3 friends and you can enjoy the game.
Click on the gadget <SPIN>, choose a consonant and so on...  
Try it and you will learn how to play. 
;-)
